Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.06,0:00:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1945年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.33,0:00:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类史上最邪恶的生物降临到这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.34,0:00:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类组成共同战线来对抗这些来访者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.28,0:00:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用最强的破坏兵器 对来访者却完全无效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.12,0:00:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国土被烟雾灰尘所污染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.86,0:00:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来访者不知何时开始被称为幻兽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.23,0:00:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类开始了漫长的消耗战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.58,0:00:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过了半个世纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.83,0:01:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西元1999年7月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.04,0:01:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第一话  来访者」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.98,0:01:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是CVα-6 距离目标上空还有60秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.55,0:01:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.99,0:01:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地天候下雨 视线范围二级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.26,0:01:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敌雷达已经开启
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.53,0:01:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行最终状况确认 行动区域为D47区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敌范围确定只有小型目标物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.20,0:01:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前锋为三号机速水 二号机泷川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.07,0:01:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后卫为四号机濑户口 以及一号机壬生屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.44,0:01:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士魂一号机请求担任前锋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.68,0:01:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求驳回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.51,0:02:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要当前锋 就多磨练射击技巧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.28,0:02:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是CVα-6 现在即将进行降落作业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.36,0:02:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.24,0:02:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各突击队已接近目标 炮兵队停止火力支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.75,0:02:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-HWT出动\N-收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.59,0:02:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全装置解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.36,0:02:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一号机正常、二号机正常\N三号机正常、四号机正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.03,0:02:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仪表板完全正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.73,0:02:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5 4 3 2 1 出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.68,0:03:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(七夕特卖)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨好大呢 真惨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.33,0:03:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大雨 所以雷达不太稳 机能大概只有七八成吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-泷川 出发咯\N-0K
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.46,0:03:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壬生屋 冷静下来 这是其他部队的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.96,0:03:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.10,0:03:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂～ 你振作一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.33,0:04:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不小心打到自己人 可不是开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.27,0:04:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不想吃子弹的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.31,0:04:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户口快来帮我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 在三点钟方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没中？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.13,0:04:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有援军 在八点钟方向！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.57,0:04:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水 小心上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是5121部队 已遭遇敌方目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.75,0:04:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 这里是5121部队 已遭遇敌方目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是北风02 已确认是幻兽主脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.53,0:05:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形式为E-1 座标576.740
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.77,0:05:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北风02已完成索敌任务 现在即刻返回护卫PBE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.28,0:05:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北风02收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.91,0:05:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.49,0:05:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪恶魔术师有说过 这里世代都被谄咒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.06,0:05:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水会变成血 草木会枯萎 虫鱼乌兽也会死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.43,0:05:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的子孙也无法微笑着面对明天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.50,0:05:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要工作咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.22,0:05:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壬生屋 快躲开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.54,0:06:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一波歼灭成功 各部队撤退 进行补给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方幻兽主脑朝东南方移动中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.85,0:06:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方主力分成两路 朝5121部队后方布阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始启动PBE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.76,0:06:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔离结束 开始启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.27,0:06:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活性化成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.21,0:06:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我困了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那上个洗手间快去睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PBE启动讯号确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PBE部队已开始行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.52,0:07:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HWT各机负责敌方机动部队 另外请避免波及市区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的哪有做的简单啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.60,0:07:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没时间抱怨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.40,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东方两公里处有河流 就暂时代替当壕沟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北风02 你太靠近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北风02 有收到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.55,0:08:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 望望美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.55,0:08:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望望美的朋友都没事喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那就先这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.84,0:09:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.08,0:09:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上六点 应该就可以再度使用PBE了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.58,0:09:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打倒主脑就会一直有增援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通宵熬夜不是常有的事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像是中大奖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.19,0:09:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.09,0:09:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是抽到下下签了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.12,0:09:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.12,0:09:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.26,0:10:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 我们的孩子似乎都平安无事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.40,0:10:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 望望美说的果然没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.64,0:10:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳野老师 我要去准备作战简报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.91,0:10:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以帮我请大叔准备晚餐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.54,0:10:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.05,0:10:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚餐请做豪华一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.55,0:10:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的任务将是负责PBE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.79,0:10:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.16,0:10:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂～今天一起去看泳衣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.43,0:10:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 难道有男朋友了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.07,0:10:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该算吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.80,0:10:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男朋友真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.31,0:10:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你这么想要男朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那里有男人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.32,0:10:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.18,0:10:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是特别班的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人只会泡妞 所以不考虑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他们再优秀 不过编在特别班就有点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.79,0:11:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 感谢您没有让我适合当驾驶员呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么说可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整备小组连络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.71,0:11:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于攻击部队已经归队 1800将进行作战简报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.71,0:11:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在十分钟之内在教室集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.35,0:11:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸的威力这么大 难道幻兽主脑没有死吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.72,0:11:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告说这次的失败是因为误爆意外所致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.99,0:11:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误爆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.63,0:11:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 明天的第二波攻击将由5121部队负责PBE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.64,0:11:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户口 有什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.37,0:11:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们一定得负责这么危险的东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.51,0:11:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要消灭主脑只能使用PBE进行零距离攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.51,0:12:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然对付头头就要用必杀技啊 我都已经热血沸腾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.38,0:12:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是电玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.15,0:12:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是既然负责PBE 就表示我们是主角啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.52,0:12:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是无忧无虑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过什么是零距离啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.66,0:12:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是把PBE直接打入主脑体内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.03,0:12:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-玩真的啊\N-听起来越来越帅气了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.54,0:12:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外PBE是非常贵重且需要长时间制造的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.27,0:12:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一启动就无法临时停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.78,0:12:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东原望望美 东原同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道启动方法了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.79,0:12:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…不对 应该说是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.06,0:12:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那之后就麻烦班长了\N-遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.56,0:12:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-首先原负责协助启动\N-遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.93,0:12:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.57,0:12:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PBE的规格书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.07,0:12:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到引爆之前的步骤就麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.44,0:13:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-天亮之前要记起来啊…\N-原学姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话 请用这个 对保养肌肤很有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.58,0:13:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.58,0:13:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请整备小组负责检查启动仪表是否正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.82,0:13:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么这样 -乖乖\N-肯定要通宵熬夜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.09,0:13:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小队编组如下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.82,0:13:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水负责搬运作业 泷川负责后方支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.46,0:13:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前锋是濑户口跟壬生屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.46,0:13:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-壬生屋同学\N-是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话先说在前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.60,0:13:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么排可不是因为你的技术啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.11,0:13:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.48,0:13:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很吵耶
