Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.85,0:13:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后会对四位驾驶员说明攻击顺序跟战术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.76,0:13:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上 解散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.99,0:13:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 真不愧是班长呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么想都觉得是最合适的人选对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.87,0:14:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.64,0:14:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过关于HWT的调整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.01,0:14:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得无论是谁来作都一定会疏忽一些细节呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真敢说啊
